liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: It was not the best second half, but Portugal got the win. They really could have won that game 6-0, but Vietnam held tough. Vietnam cannot make it through to the Round of 16. Thier match against the Netherlands will be their last in this tournament.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: FULL-TIME: Portugal defeat Vietnam 2-0

children.content: It was not the best second half, but Portugal got the win.
They really could have won that game 6-0, but Vietnam held tough.
Vietnam cannot make it through to the Round of 16. Thier match against the Netherlands will be their last in this tournament.
